{"tid":2100084,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪真係無方法令一個人變得體貼？","createTime":"2020-07-08T19:05:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T20:00:12.000Z","uid":309102,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a00cb684d42416a8123798457f9e42d1a73b451f","tid":2100084,"uid":309102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T19:05:48.000Z","msg":"男朋友係嗰啲覺得同朋友出去玩 (包括收工去約人食個飯)<br />\n只要唔係返工 翻到黎係冇資格講攰嘅人 <br />\n有時想同佢求其呻幾句 聽下佢氹都好似好難咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時我唔小心喺路到kick親 正常見到都會問句有冇事<br />\n但係佢真係好自然咁 第一時間就問我又搞乜 可唔可以小心啲行路<br />\n其實都係想佢可以體貼少少姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd091d8be9fa754a2e9f85dc3d3ebf96a39d559a","tid":2100084,"uid":262747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T19:07:10.000Z","msg":"係 分手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fadcd9e5cfcfea283aec2276037667aa254c7eee","tid":2100084,"uid":326758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T19:08:58.000Z","msg":"係 分手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a8b7d7826f9597d2a8f7eea2fa874e1524dfa1c","tid":2100084,"uid":134103,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T19:14:39.000Z","msg":"呢啲係性格嘅一種嚟，江山易改本性難移，唔會話冇得改嘅，但係機會微乎其微囉<br />\n<br />\n正如大家都知風趣幽默嘅男人溝女有着數，所以間唔中就會見到有連登仔開po問點先可以變得幽默，實際上風趣幽默亦係一個性格特點，九成都係天生嘅，冇得強求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c9741d818bf636a7d50d1f53c9124b02603ae86","tid":2100084,"uid":15948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T19:28:39.000Z","msg":"有方法 同我一齊"},{"pid":"43b37136d077a70fab22470804a40f0eddcf0835","tid":2100084,"uid":38383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T20:00:12.000Z","msg":"幾似我 kick親冇跌姐係冇事啦"}]}